{
  "stem": "4570.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he spoke to me in Czech.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I-- I spoke a little bit Czech.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he-- he sort of was chummy with me over the phone.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when he heard I was being sacked, he gave me a job as his secretary.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I couldn't type.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I couldn't do shorthand.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I worked for quite a long time and did his correspondence.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I learned how to write in short-- not shorthand, but my own abbreviations and dictation.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he couldn't speak properly [LAUGHS] German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I couldn't speak Czech.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But-- but it worked out all right.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So-- so, I mean, I was working right up, I think, till one week till I went to the camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I met my boyfriend.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His name is Hans Selig.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But because we were all into Hollywood things and-- and Ginger Rogers and Fred Astaire.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Hans definitely did not agree to me, so I Christianed him Goldie.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was a blind date.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we met in-- in June, 1939.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was just more than-- a little bit over 16, and he was just a little bit over 17.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we just fell in love.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we had-- we, you know, we had-- we had a wonderful time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't let all-- all the misery disturb our-- that was the first love for both for us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So it-- it-- it-- it-- it was very, very important to us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He had just come back in 1939 from a holiday in England.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And his parents, who were millionaires, who had a private bank, who had blocks of land all over Prague, let that boy come back in 1939 after we were already occupied by the Germans, instead of writing to him-- stay in England.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it-- it was-- I was happy I met him.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
